  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years old.

          -  Currently Pregnant

          -  High risk of pre-term birth in the periviable period 20+0 to 25+6 wga

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Intrauterine Fetal Demise (prior to admission)

          -  Inability to read or communicate in english
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
